N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4215.10 - Machines locked at off-time

State Regulations

The pari-mutuel machines will be locked by the judges
immediately upon the opening of the stall doors of the starting gate on the
signal of the starter. Notes
